        <p id="Header">
            A New Approach to NHL Equivalency:  <br>
            Redefining Conversion Factors and Prospect Projections
    
        <p id="Content">
            Discover a new NHLe (NHL equivalency) model that measures the value of one point in other leagues relative to the NHL. It considers the various pathways that prospects undertake on their journey to the NHL and provides accurate point projection for players. 
        </p>

        <p id="Link">
            For a detailed analysis, click the link below. Scroll down for a quick summary. 
        </p>

        <a href = "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1oOG1_uPFuV01W38UdpZssxEsAk-pHd6l/view?usp=sharing">
